title: The Taj Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Everyday at lunchtime is an all-you-can-eat buffet. The a la carte lunch and dinner menu includes some vegetarian entrees plus assorted breads, rice, and appetizers. Vegans should specify as ghee/dairy is used. Nice atmosphere, decorated with Indian-themed paintings on the walls.
